  "body": "# Feature Issue\n\n[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\n\n### User Story\n\nAs a user, I want tx history to be fetched in the background to receive notifications and to be aware about incoming transfers. \n\n### Description\n\nThe app keeps checking history every N minutes (currently 20) while it is in the background. In case if user spent more than M minutes (3 currently) in the background and opened the app again we check history. If user quickly changed context (put app to the background, checked something in another app, went back to Status) the app doesn't check history just to avoid making unnecessary requests.   \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n\nTransfers are fetched while app is in the background, PNs are shown. \n\n### Notes\n\nAndroid only feature for now.",
